/**
 * WorkHistory component (formerly ProjectTimeline).
 * Real CV work history entries with journey-style scroll animations.
 * - Timeline line draws progressively as user scrolls
 * - Dots pulse and glow when entries come into view
 * - Content slides in with staggered reveal
 */

